  <h1 class="anotherhead" id="recruitment"><%= Date.today.year.to_s() + s+ "RECRUITMENT INFORMATION"%></h1>
  <p>DAS accepts applications biannually, at the start of the fall semester and the spring semester. Please look out for more information pertaining to recruitment in the coming weeks and do not hesitate to reach out to DAS leadership with any questions or concerns.</p>
  <p>Application Link: <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfdG5ZKRINxVEKWjR0f2pJsJGtx6aMmbK9BT9CMZ29RJyeviw/viewform">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfdG5ZKRINxVEKWjR0f2pJsJGtx6</a></p>
  <p>For general inquiries, please fill in the following contact form:</p>
  <form class="needs-validation" novalidate role="form" id="reused_form" action="/submit">
    <%= token_tag %> 
    <div class="form-row" id="name">
      <div class="col">
        <label for="invalidCheck">First Name:</label>
        <input type="text" name="first_name" class="form-control" placeholder="First name" id="first_name" required>
        <div class="invalid-feedback">
          First name is required.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <label for="invalidCheck">Last Name:</label>
        <input type="text" name="last_name" class="form-control" placeholder="Last name" id="last_name" required>
        <div class="invalid-feedback">
          Last name is required.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="invalidCheck">Email address:</label>
      <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Enter email" id="enter_email" required>
      <div class="invalid-feedback">
        Email is required.
      </div>
      <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</small>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="invalidCheck">Message:</label>
      <textarea name="message" class="form-control" rows=5 id="enter_message" required></textarea>
      <div class="invalid-feedback">
        Message is required.
      </div>
    </div>
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark">Submit</button>
  </form>
</div>

